T.query: select e.emp_no as emp_no ,de.emp_no as dept_emp_emp_no,s.emp_no as s_emp_no, s.from_date as s_from_date, d.dept_no, t.emp_no as t_emp_no, t.title, t.from_date as t_from_date from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no left join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date join dept_emp de on de.emp_no = e.emp_no join departments d on de.dept_no = d.dept_no where e.emp_no = 231013
